Package: vpdsus
Title: Vaccine Preventable Disease Susceptibility Estimation and Risk Scanning
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Oliver", "Watson", email = "ojwatson@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Tools to retrieve WHO GHO immunisation coverage and reported cases,
    combine them with demography, estimate susceptibility via progressive methods,
    produce WHO-style ranking plots, and link susceptibility to outbreak risk.
    Implements a fully reproducible workflow with caching and analysis scaffolding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
